Prosím? Dom Fujiwara.

7
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:42,630
Oh, to si ty, Natsume.

8
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:43,290
Ako sa máš?

9
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:47,150
Eh, kto je tam?

10
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:48,780
Čo? To si ma nespoznal?

11
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,160
Shibata!

12
